  "stem": "<p>Triangle <math alttext=\"upper A upper B upper C\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>A</mi>\n\t<mi>B</mi>\n\t<mi>C</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math> is similar to triangle <math alttext=\"upper D upper E upper F\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>D</mi>\n\t<mi>E</mi>\n\t<mi>F</mi>\n</mrow>\n</math>, where angle <math alttext=\"upper A\"><mi>A</mi>\n</math> corresponds to angle <math alttext=\"upper D\"><mi>D</mi>\n</math>, and angles<em> </em><math alttext=\"upper C\"><mi>C</mi>\n</math> and <math alttext=\"upper F\"><mi>F</mi>\n</math> are right angles. If <math alttext=\"cosine upper B equals one twenty second\"><mi>cos</mi><mi>B</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>22</mn></mfrac></math>, what is the value of <math alttext=\"cosine upper E\"><mi>cos</mi><mi>E</mi></math>?</p>",
